  ('optician-moex-00499', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '將-5.00DS的透鏡置於左眼，若要產生2Δ基底朝外的稜鏡量，要如何移心？', '["向外偏心4mm", "向內偏心4mm", "向外偏心2mm", "向內偏心2mm"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e5804bd33054", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5a711a9edcd0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
