  ('optician-moex-00501', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某鏡片的度數為+2.00DS/-1.00DC×180，將其磨成正柱面形式。若選擇+5.00D的基弧，則其後弧應為 幾度？', '["-3.00D", "-4.00D", "-5.00D", "-6.00D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e5804bd33054", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5a711a9edcd0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00502', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '個案兩眼皆為-4.00DS/-1.00DC×180，若要使左眼產生2ΔBU，左眼鏡片的光學中心點與右眼的相對位 置為何？', '["左眼比右眼的光心高2cm", "左眼比右眼的光心高2mm", "左眼比右眼的光心低4cm", "左眼比右眼的光心低4mm"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e5804bd33054", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5a711a9edcd0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00503', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '以CR-39樹脂（n=1.5）磨製一個新月形的球面鏡片毛坯（lensblank），前表面的曲率半徑為+50cm， 則前表面的屈光力為何？', '["+1.00D", "-1.00D", "+1.50D", "-1.50D"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e5804bd33054", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5a711a9edcd0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00504', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '調整鏡架時，依據下列何種調整方式使鏡架遠離臉部？', '["增加前傾角", "調寬鼻墊", "減少鼻墊壁的有效長度", "減少鏡框彎弧"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e5804bd33054", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5a711a9edcd0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0909", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00505', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於硬式及軟式隱形鏡片之淚液交換何者錯誤？', '["水凝膠鏡片每次眨眼只能交換大約1%的淚液體積", "硬式鏡片每次眨眼最多可以交換20%的淚液體積", "GP（gaspermeable）鏡片與同等厚度的水凝膠鏡片相比，GP鏡片能夠向角膜輸送2至3倍的氧氣", "水凝膠鏡片與同等厚度的GP鏡片相比，水凝膠鏡片比GP鏡片較能夠向角膜輸送8至10倍的氧氣"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5763fac48738", "answer_pdf_sha1": "feb21889645c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00506', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者較不適合戴lowDkF-S/A（fluoro-silicone/acrylate）硬式透氣鏡片？', '["長期GP配戴者，TBUT為8秒，鏡片有黏蛋白膜（mucoproteinfilm）", "度數-4.00DS/-3.00DC×180者", "軟式鏡片配戴者，經歷過鏡片沉積物問題（引起發紅、發癢和配戴時間減少）導致巨大乳突結膜炎", "雙眼度數+8.00DS/-1.00DC×180者"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5763fac48738", "answer_pdf_sha1": "feb21889645c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0908", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
